    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know i should talk to them but i've already had my blood work done lately and the levels were totally fine. it feels like i'm being overmedicated when i feel so healthy. if my numbers are stable, wouldn't a lower dose like 2mg be a logical way to just maintain that balance without the risk of maybe bleeding too much? it seems safer to go lower than to stay on a high dose if i don't need it.",
